oai_dc:dc.dc:title: Synthesis of functionalized cis-syn-cis triquinanes
oai_dc:dc.dc:creator: KOTHA, S
MANIVANNAN, E
oai_dc:dc.dc:description: Functionalized cis-syn-cis triquinane ring systems are identified as useful precursors to higher polyquinanes. In this regard, two strategies to prepare thine triquinane ring systems from caged compounds are described.
oai_dc:dc.dc:identifier: INDIAN JOURNAL OF CHEMISTRY SECTION B-ORGANIC CHEMISTRY INCLUDING MEDICINAL CHEMISTRY, 41(4), 808-811
